<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Na lungsietna thuphan ka lung gilo a zo,
 Pathien khawvel hehpih A cha neihsun A pie'i.

[V2]
 Kuole Amah gingcha ta chun,
 Kumsawt hinna aneih nang-un (2)

[V3]
 2. Dakgul khaihkang khan, hinna, damna a pie thei,
 Kross chunga Lal Isun ena hing din ei hilh.

[V4]
 3. Gitloh man chuh thihna, Beimang ka hih ka hei,
 Kumsawta mangthai san, Na hehpih thu ka zai.

[V5]
 4. Khawvel thiemloh chansak di'n, Krista A hung puoi,
 A min zieka Hukdam ahih na'n A hung zawi.

[V6]
 5. Lalpa, ka ginlahna hi ei hung panpih in!
 Na chanchin phu thugen ginga muonna nei di'n.</lyrics>
<title>THE GOSPEL OF THY GRACE</title>
</song>